Privacy Policy:

Date: December 2020

What information does the app collect?

We collect none of your information nor do we share any of your information with 3rd parties.

Why do we require permission?

1- Internet Permission: You should connect to the Internet to broadcast the Radio stations.

2- Record Audio Permission: This permission is required to display an audio equalizer(and you can ignore it if you want, but the equalizer will not be displayed).

3- Read Phone state Permission: This permission is required for stopping the broadcast when the phone receives any incoming calls.

4- Access network state Permission: Required to check the status of the network to change the functionality of the app.

